      • run

        public void run()
        This method processes each image file supplied using Zxing library and finds the barcode results using different readers for Code 39, QR and Datamatrix formats. Permissible barcode reader types are configurable and defined in database.
        Parameters:
        sourceImage - BufferedImage
        fileName - String
        appReaderTypes - String[]
        Throws:
        DCMAApplicationException
